Datum is a fast modern database viewer. This has all the features and speed of itâ€™s predecessor and is FREE! Quickly view your data and modifying table schema.
This app is perfect for anyone who deals with SQLite. Especially those who are just looking to browse or only need to import or export data as it is by far the cheapest, most powerful option on the App Store.

What's new in version 7.0.1:
- Fixed bug with semicolons in SQL view.
- Sped up SQL queries.
- Allows for multiple column sorting.
- Smarter updating of columns.
- Fixes editing a row filled with NULL's.
- Fixes Filtering in log.
- Import data directly into a new table.
- Allows for inputing very very very large numbers as Strings.
- Fixes opening the edit view to the column clicked.
- Fixes some font scaling issues.
